meta.name: Virtual Services-Template
meta.description: template created from dashboard: Virtual Services

queries.text:
from(bucket: "axf")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "RsConnrate")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["Custid"] == v.CustID)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["Lmclusterid"] == v.LoadMasterClusterID)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["VSID"] == v.VirtualServiceID)
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")
